-- Xolo - Nationwide online accounting service for freelancers
('Xolo', 'Tax/Accounting', 'All-in-one online accounting service designed specifically for freelancers (autónomos) in Spain. Formerly known as LeapIN. Combines an easy-to-use digital platform with a team of expert accountants to handle invoicing, expense tracking, tax compliance, and quarterly/annual tax filings. Specializes in helping both Spanish and international freelancers navigate the complexities of Spanish tax regulations. Services include free autónomo registration with Hacienda and Social Security within 24 hours, automated invoice creation with VAT calculation, deductible expense management, and personalized support from dedicated account managers. English-speaking support available via email. Uses the CIRCE system for telematic procedures and is a collaborating entity with the Agencia Tributaria (Spanish Tax Agency) and member of ASEFIGET. Serves freelancers nationwide through their online platform. Ideal for digital nomads, remote workers, and professionals in consulting, IT, marketing, creative services, teaching, translation, and other service-based industries. Various pricing plans available including Lite (self-service), Starter, Global (for international clients), and Premium tiers.', 'Carrer de Muntaner 239, Àtic', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', NULL, 'info@xolo.io', 'https://www.xolo.io/es-en', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
